      <title>日本自民党主席玉城力挺减税要求 力挺陷入困境的自民党</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-31/japan-s-tamaki-digs-in-over-tax-demand-to-support-ailing-ldp</link>
